        {
            "title": "軟件股風聲鶴唳之際 高盛推出「抗AI替代」主題股票籃子",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 高盛推出了一個新的定制股票籃子，旨在應對軟件股日益加劇的動盪局面，押注那些被認為比其他公司更能抵禦<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>顛覆的企業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司推出了一個軟件板塊的配對交易籃子：做多那些被認為難以被人工智能取代的公司 —— 要麼因為其業務需要實體執行，要麼因其受到監管壁壘保護，或涉及必須由人承擔責任的環節 —— 同時做空那些其工作流程可能越來越多被人工智能自動化或在內部被復制替代的企業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在做多方面，高盛青睞能直接受益於人工智能普及的企業，包括計算服務、數據基礎設施、可觀測性解決方案、網絡安全、超大規模雲服務及人工智能開發平台的供應商。該籃子涵蓋Cloudflare Inc.、CrowdStrike Holdings Inc.、派拓網絡、甲骨文和微軟等公司。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d1c98925-527f-3363-a6fa-5b6dc643dd1c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">做空方面，交易員瞄準了可能因人工智能能力擴展而被自動化或內部重建的軟件傾向型工作流程。相關標的包括Monday.com Ltd.、Salesforce Inc.、DocuSign Inc.、埃森哲和多鄰國。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛美國定制籃子團隊副總裁Faris Mourad在致客戶報告中指出，「我們預計該籃子的做多部分將從近期軟件板塊拋售中復甦，而做空部分將滯後。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vGLLGhYO40k36IZHy2f6fQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6ddc01c7a00af22b6abf83f0248be86d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Traders Launch AI-Proof Software Basket Amid Sector Rout</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E8%82%A1%E9%A2%A8%E8%81%B2%E9%B6%B4%E5%94%B3%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA-%E6%8A%97ai%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E7%B1%83%E5%AD%90-175409652.html",
